    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since its inception in 2022, MANORS has been on a relentless mission to redefine golf, taking it far from the traditional clubhouse setting and into the wild. Their journey has not only reimagined what golf can be but has also pushed the boundaries of performance wear and style both on and off the course. Now, as MANORS prepares to release the fourth and final volume of their groundbreaking Frontier Collection, they take us further afield than ever before, to the breathtaking and untamed beauty of Lofoten Links \u2013 the most northerly links course in the world.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["text_1"],
      "settings": {
