    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Journey to the Edge: The Spirit of the Frontier Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since launching The Frontier Collection, MANORS has challenged the conventional golf aesthetic by blending rugged outdoor adventure with cutting-edge sportswear. This ethos is perfectly encapsulated in their choice of Lofoten Links as the backdrop for Volume IV. Nestled deep within the Arctic Circle, Lofoten Links is not just a golf course; it\u2019s a testament to the wild and wonderful potential of the game. Carved into the rugged Norwegian coastline, this course defies expectations, offering a golf experience that is as breathtaking as it is challenging.</p><p>MANORS has always sought to take golf beyond the manicured lawns of traditional clubs, and their Frontier Collection has symbolised this philosophy in both design and execution. Each volume of the collection has drawn inspiration from remote, untamed locations, and Lofoten Links, with its dramatic fjords and stunning vistas, is the perfect final chapter. This is more than just sportswear; it\u2019s a celebration of golf\u2019s wild frontier.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
