    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Ranger Track Golf Jacket and Trousers: A Revolution in Sportswear",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At the heart of Volume IV lies the standout look of the Autumn/Winter collection: The Ranger Track Golf Jacket and matching Trousers. Available in a sleek Taupe and Navy as well as a striking Burgundy and Taupe combination, this two-piece ensemble is designed to reimagine the classic tracksuit for the modern golf athlete.</p><p>The Ranger Golf Track Jacket features raglan sleeves and woven nylon fabric, providing maximum movement and comfort without compromising on style. This combination is a bold statement from MANORS, challenging the traditional dress codes of golf with a design that is both functional and fashionable. The inclusion of raglan sleeves ensures that the garment moves with the wearer, whether navigating the rugged terrain of Lofoten or simply swinging through 18 holes.</p><p>Nick Watts, Head of Product at MANORS, explains the significance of this design:</p><p><em>\u201cGolf has always been too precious for the full tracksuit but these days golfers are athletes: They should be allowed to dress like them. I think the Ranger Golf Jacket and Pant combination will provoke traditional clubs to reconsider what qualifies as appropriate sportswear for the course.\u201d</em></p><p>This statement encapsulates the ethos of the entire Frontier Collection \u2013 a desire to break down the barriers between the golf course and the real world, creating a wardrobe that speaks to the needs of today\u2019s athlete. The Ranger ensemble is not just clothing; it\u2019s a manifesto for a new era in golf fashion.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
