    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Eighteenth Ranger Polo: Bold Design Meets Superior Functionality",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The final volume of the Frontier Collection also introduces the Eighteenth Ranger Polo, arguably the boldest polo design MANORS has ever released. Available in Taupe and Navy, the polo features the MANORS emblem in a repeater pattern that is as striking as it is stylish.</p><p>The Eighteenth Ranger Polo is designed with the athlete in mind, incorporating a four-way stretching upper back panel to support the golf swing, a feature that ensures flexibility and comfort without sacrificing form. The modern quarter zip adds a contemporary touch, while the ribbed sleeves and cuffs maintain the classic polo structure, making this piece versatile enough for both on and off the course.</p><p>Temperature control is another key feature of this polo, with brushed-back fabric ensuring warmth during cool autumn rounds \u2013 a necessity when playing in the Arctic Circle. This attention to detail highlights MANORS\u2019 commitment to creating apparel that is not only stylish but also incredibly functional.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
