    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The End of a Journey, the Beginning of a Legacy",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As MANORS prepares to release the fourth and final volume of The Frontier Collection, they do so with the knowledge that they have pushed the boundaries of what golf apparel can be. From the rugged landscapes of the world\u2019s most remote courses to the cutting-edge design of their apparel, MANORS has redefined the sport, taking it out of the clubhouse and into the wild.</p><p>The Ranger Golf Jacket and Trousers, the Eighteenth Ranger Polo, and the stunning campaign shot at Lofoten Links are more than just the culmination of The Frontier Collection; they are a statement of intent. MANORS is not just a brand \u2013 it\u2019s a movement, one that will continue to challenge the status quo and redefine the game of golf for years to come.</p><p>As we look forward to the release of Volume IV, it\u2019s clear that this is just the beginning of MANORS\u2019 legacy. The final chapter of The Frontier Collection may be closing, but the journey of taking golf into the wild is far from over. With MANORS leading the way, the future of golf looks more exciting than ever.</p>"
          }
        },
